A 10-year old class one pupil at Losuk Primary School is recuperating at Maralal Referral Hospital after sustaining serious injuries in her private parts, after she was allegedly ambushed and raped by a man. According to her mother; Irene Lenguleiy, her daughter arrived home safe after school and went to fetch water from a near by water source, when she was attacked and raped by a man whom she was able to identify. 